tactical_recommendations: ⚠️ HIGH COORDINATION DETECTED: Avoid trading against synchronized whale movements. Wait for coordination breakdown.
🎯 MULTIPLE HIT-AND-RUN OPERATORS: Use limit orders, avoid market orders during their ambush hours.
🎖️ Sun Tzu: 'In the midst of chaos, there is also opportunity.' Trade when whales are fighting each other.
🇮🇪 IRA: 'Hit and run. Small, precise strikes. Never overstay your welcome.'
🪶 Apache: 'Patience. Know the terrain. Wait for the perfect moment.'
